<div class="privacy-policy-page">
  <h1>The Aerotagejobs.com Web Site Privacy Policy</h1>

  <%= image_tag 'privacy_policy.png' %>

  <p class="justified">
    The privacy, confidence, and trust of individuals who visit Aerotagejobs.com are important to us. No personal information is collected at this site unless it is provided
    voluntarily by an individual while participating in an activity that asks for the information. The following paragraphs disclose the information gathering and usage
