    This website has links to many other web sites. These include links to websites operated by government agencies, nonprofit organizations, and private businesses. Neither
    Aerotagejobs.com nor Aerotage Design Group, Inc. is responsible for the content or privacy practices of these sites and suggests you review their privacy statements.
  </p>
  <h2>Contact Information</h2>
  <p>
    Aerotage Design Group, Inc. welcomes comments regarding this privacy statement. Please convey any questions or concerns to: admin@aerotagejobs.com or P.O. Box 1026 Central,
